    "en": {
      "title": "Water cut tonight (20)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The National Water Supply and Drainage Board says that the water supply to many areas of Colombo will be suspended for 10 hours from 11:00 pm tonight (20) until 9:00 am tomorrow (21).",
        "Accordingly, the water supply to Colombo 05 and 06 areas will be suspended for 10 hours.",
        "The NWS&DB stated that the water supply will be provided to Colombo 04 areas under a low pressure during the same period.",
        "The water supply interruption will be carried out due to essential improvement work."
      ],
